       "Ten minutes. No coding. No design skills. No Squarespace. No Wix. Let's build a professional website with AI and deploy it to the internet.\n\nMinute 1-2: Content generation. Open Claude or ChatGPT. Prompt: 'Generate all content for a locksmith business website in Destin Florida. Include: hero section, services list with descriptions, about section, service areas, pricing guide, FAQ with 10 questions, and contact information.' The AI generates 2,000 words of professional content in 30 seconds.\n\nMinute 3-5: Build the site. We use a Python script with aiohttp that generates a complete HTML website from the AI content. One command, full website with responsive design, proper SEO meta tags, schema markup, and modern styling. Our system builds sites with 12 sections and 1,900+ words per page.\n\nMinute 6-7: Add the AI chatbot. Embed our chat widget with a single script tag. Now every visitor gets instant AI-powered customer service. The chatbot knows your services, pricing, and can book appointments.\n\nMinute 8-9: Deploy. Use Cloudflare Tunnel to put it on the internet with a custom domain. Free SSL certificate included. Takes 2 minutes to set up.\n\nMinute 10: SEO. Add Google Analytics, submit sitemap to Google Search Console, set up Google Business Profile. Your site is now discoverable.\n\nWe built 63 websites this way. Each one customized for a different city and service. All 63 in one afternoon. They rank for local keywords, have AI chatbots, and generate leads automatically.\n\nThe entire stack is free. Python, aiohttp, Cloudflare free tier, AI chat. Zero monthly costs.\n\nCode and templates in the description. Go build your site.",
       "Speed-run screen recording of entire process. Before/after: blank terminal to live website. Mobile view of finished site. Chat widget demo. Google search results.",
       "Laptop showing beautiful website. Stopwatch overlay showing '10:00'. Text 'NO CODE NEEDED'. Impressed expression pointing at screen.",
       "build website AI,AI website builder,free website builder,no code website,website in 10 minutes,AI web development,Python website,aiohttp website,free website 2026,website tutorial,AI powered website,website with chatbot,deploy website free,Cloudflare tunnel,small business website,locksmith website,service business website,SEO website,hive dynamics,AI web design",
       "Build a professional AI-powered website in under 10 minutes. No coding, no monthly fees, includes AI chatbot. Full tutorial with code.\n\nhivecore.app/website-builder\n#WebDev #NoCode #AI #WebsiteBuilder #Tutorial",
       "Grab the code from the pinned comment. Subscribe for more rapid-build tutorials.",
