       "We went from zero leads to 138 qualified leads in one month using nothing but AI. Zero ad spend. Here's the exact system.",
       "1. The lead gen stack\n2. Content-based lead gen\n3. AI cold outreach\n4. Chatbot lead capture\n5. Phone lead capture\n6. Qualification and scoring\n7. Results after 30 days",
       "One hundred and thirty-eight qualified leads in 30 days. Zero dollars in advertising. Pure AI-powered lead generation. Let me break down exactly how we did it.\n\nThe stack: AI content generation for SEO. AI cold email outreach. AI chatbot on 63 websites. AI phone agent on our main line. AI lead scoring to prioritize follow-up.\n\nContent-based lead gen: We used AI to generate 400+ pages of locally-optimized content. Blog posts targeting keywords like 'locksmith near me Destin FL', 'emergency lockout service Fort Walton Beach', '24 hour locksmith Pensacola'. Each page is unique, 1,900+ words, with embedded calls to action. Google started ranking these pages within 2 weeks.\n\nAI cold outreach: Our AI researches property management companies, real estate agents, and commercial building managers. It generates personalized emails referencing their specific properties and needs. We sent 500 emails. 40% open rate. 12% clicked. 3.2% booked a call.\n\nChatbot capture: Every one of our 63 websites has an AI chatbot. When someone asks about pricing or availability, the chatbot collects their name, phone, address, and specific need. That's a qualified lead captured at 2 AM while we sleep.\n\nPhone lead capture: Our AI phone agent answers every call. It captures caller information, determines their need, and either books an appointment immediately or adds them to our follow-up queue.\n\nLead scoring: AI analyzes each lead based on service needed, location, urgency, and engagement level. Hot leads get immediate follow-up. Warm leads enter a nurture sequence.\n\n30-day results: 138 total leads. 89 from organic search. 23 from cold email. 18 from chatbot. 8 from phone. Estimated pipeline value: $87,000.\n\nThis system runs 24/7 with zero human involvement in lead capture. We just handle the actual service calls.",
