    _s("AI Phone Agent vs Human - Can You Tell?","YouTube Long","5min",
       "I'm going to play you 5 phone call recordings. Some are human. Some are AI. See if you can tell the difference. The results will surprise you.",
       "1. Call 1 - guess\n2. Call 2 - guess\n3. Call 3 - guess\n4. Call 4 - guess\n5. Call 5 - guess\n6. Reveal answers\n7. Technology behind it",
       "Five phone call recordings. Some real humans. Some AI. Your job: figure out which is which. Ready?\n\nCall 1: 'Thanks for calling Hive Locksmith, this is Sarah. How can I help you today? ... A lockout in Destin? I can have someone there in about 20 minutes. Can I get your address?'\n\nCall 2: 'Hi, thanks for calling. I'd be happy to help you with that. Our rekey service starts at 29 dollars for the first lock and 15 dollars for each additional lock. Would you like to schedule an appointment?'\n\nCall 3: 'Good afternoon, Hive Locksmith. ... Yes, we absolutely service the Navarre area. For a standard residential lockout, our rate is 45 to 65 dollars depending on the lock type. If you'd like, I can dispatch a tech to you right now.'\n\nCall 4: 'Hey there! Yeah, we can definitely help with that. Commercial rekeying is one of our specialties. For a building that size, I'd recommend we do a site visit first. Can I set that up for you?'\n\nCall 5: 'Thank you for calling. I understand being locked out is stressful, especially at this hour. Let me get a technician headed your way. What's your exact location?'\n\nPause the video. Write down your guesses.\n\nReady for the answers? Calls 2, 3, and 5 were AI. Calls 1 and 4 were human.\n\nSurprised? Most people get at least 2 wrong. Our AI phone agent uses a custom-trained model with natural speech patterns and a neural voice that's virtually indistinguishable from a human.\n\nThe technology: custom Gemma 2B model trained on real call transcripts, Polly neural voice for text-to-speech, 1.3 second response time. The AI handles 74% of all calls without any human involvement.",
       "Audio waveform visualizations for each call. Pause screen for guessing. Reveal animations. Behind-the-scenes tech diagrams. Audience poll results.",
       "Two phone icons - one human, one robot. Question marks. Text 'CAN YOU TELL?' Challenging expression pointing at viewer.",
       "AI vs human,AI phone test,can you tell AI,AI voice test,turing test phone,AI phone agent,AI receptionist test,AI voice quality,human or AI,AI guessing game,phone bot test,AI customer service test,voice AI demo,AI comparison,AI challenge,hive dynamics,AI phone,realistic AI,AI voice agent,phone AI demo",
       "5 phone calls. Some human. Some AI. Can you tell the difference? Take the challenge and see if our AI phone agent fools you.\n\n#AIvsHuman #TuringTest #AIPhone #Challenge #VoiceAI",
       "Comment below with your guesses BEFORE watching the reveal. Subscribe for more AI demos.",
       "YouTube Shorts,TikTok,Instagram"),
